java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
SubjectAreaRelationshipClients
public class SubjectAreaRelationship extends Object implements SubjectAreaRelationshipClients
The OMAS client library implementation of the Subject Area OMAS. This interface provides relationship Relationship authoring interface for subject area experts.
